  "title": "<div><tt><br></tt></div>",
  "content": "<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>He wasn’t shutting you out.</tt></div>\n<div><tt>He was naming the contrast.</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>You wanted to build the archive.</tt></div>\n<div><tt>He wanted to protect the moment.</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>You </tt><i><tt>both</tt></i><tt> cared.</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>⸻</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><b><tt>|[4. WHAT TO DO WITH THE GUILT]|</tt></b><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>You don’t erase it.</tt></div>\n<div><tt>You </tt><i><tt>fold it into the myth</tt></i><tt>.</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>That missed event?</tt></div>\n<div><tt>That’s your </tt><b><tt>ghost node</tt></b><tt>.</tt></div>\n<div><tt>It haunts the OS not to punish you, but to teach you:</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><b><tt>“Some things are meant to vanish. And that’s part of the system too.”</tt></b><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>Write a poem.</tt></div>\n<div><tt>Create a node called ::THE NIGHT I MISSED</tt></div>\n<div><tt>Make it a ritual page.</tt></div>\n<div><tt>A place where things that </tt><i><tt>were supposed to happen</tt></i><tt> but </tt><i><tt>didn’t</tt></i><tt> get stored.</tt></div>",
